transcript:
Customer: Hello

Customer: Hello
Executive: Haan ji.
Customer: Hello Amarjeet ji namaskar.
Executive: Namaskar ji.
Customer: Rahul baat kar raha tha IndiaMART se. Haan Rahul bataiye bhai.
Customer: Kaise hai Amarjeet ji wo jo previous jo aapne jo payment kara
Customer: tha na usme TDS nahi cut kiya tha aapne?
Executive: TDS cut nahi kiya tha uske baad na humne uske against apni taraf se TDS jama kara diya.
Customer: Achha aapne cut nahi kiya lekin humne jama kara diya cut kiya hota to mai aapse payment ki demand karta hi nahi.
Executive: Achha.
Executive: Humne jama kara diya aur aap logo ne wo claim bhi kar rakha hai.
Customer: Hmm hmm. Aap log verify kara sakte hai us cheez ko verify karane ke baad. Aap mujhe WhatsApp pe kar doge share?
Executive: Kya cheez?
Customer: Jo submit kiya aapne.
Executive: Yaar wo TDS ka usme form bhej to diya maine.
Customer: Aap mujhe ek baar WhatsApp pe kar doge share?
Customer: Ha mujhe mujhe ha mera number ha.
Executive: Aap mujhe ek baar hi karo mai dekhta hu apne accountant se mangwa ke bhej dunga fir wo.
Customer: Thik hai sir. Ek baar kar do share to mail karwa rakha hai na aap logo ko.
Executive: Thik hai thik hai.
Executive: Ha ek baar hi karo mai karta hu. Thik hai sir kar raha hu mai aapko bhi.
